CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Promenade - Nothing like a stroll down the Avenue on Easter Sunday. Misses Myrna Aiken and Rosemarie Lawrence turn on the personality as they brighten Centre Avenue.-Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Myrna Aiken and Rosemarie Lawrence walking along sidewalk on Centre Avenue by Falk School, University of Pittsburgh, Oakland
